#day34 #circuitbreakersg #stayhomesg 
Took out the barber shop activity I made with toilet roll. She kind of enjoyed it but gave up half way and ask me if she can use hands to help them trim instead 😂😂 She decided to pluck out their hair. Wahahaha

She was overall good today except that that her cheekiness really made us 🙄🙄🙄 don’t know how many times a day. Please remember that you are 3 not 13. Don’t talk like a 13.
